<lb ed="C I" n="0241a00"/><mulu level="1" label="之二　碑陰" type="其他"/><head>之二　碑陰</head>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a01"/><p id="pI01p0241a0101">　　　　　　　勸化主馮暉賓
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a02"/>大齊武平元年歲次庚寅正月乙
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a03"/>酉朔廿六日。
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a04"/>蓋諸佛智海。本自無<note n="0241001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31092;＝住【史】</note><app n="0241001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">住</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31092;</rdg></app>。既與法界
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a05"/>淨寬。復共虛空<note n="0241002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB11265;＝競【史】</note><app n="0241002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">競</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB11265;</rdg></app>遠。如童尊重。臥
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a06"/>渥而布髮。藥王思報。上天而雨花。
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a07"/>暮<note n="0241003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31093;＝彼【史】</note><app n="0241003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彼</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31093;</rdg></app>前縱。更開後轍。是以都邑主
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a08"/>董洪達。其人可謂映望遠聞。聲標
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a09"/><note n="0241004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31094;＝暇【史】</note><app n="0241004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">暇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31094;</rdg></app>尒。志超雲外。深識無邊。體同聚
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a10"/>沫。豈齊風露。遂率邑徒卌人等。乃
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a11"/>訪濫田美玉。琨<note n="0241005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31095;＝璞【史】</note><app n="0241005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">璞</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31095;</rdg></app>京珍。敬寫靈儀。
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a12"/>用深表代。匠思<note n="0241006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31096;＝命【史】</note><app n="0241006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">命</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31096;</rdg></app>端。朝研殊毒。畫
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a13"/>採金菕C玉鏤周畢。<note n="0241007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31100;＝眾【史】</note><app n="0241007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">眾</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31100;</rdg></app>事明麗。尋形
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a14"/>叵遍。狀若天上降來。俊似地中湧
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a15"/>出。其處　徘徊。此巖<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">霧</unclear><note n="0241008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00117;＝澗【史】</note><app n="0241008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">澗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00117;</rdg></app>。左依山
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a16"/><note n="0241009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">淭＝渠【史】</note><app n="0241009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">渠</lem><rdg wit="【原】">淭</rdg></app>。南<note n="0241010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00440;＝窺【史】</note><app n="0241010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">窺</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00440;</rdg></app>大路。西<note n="0241011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31097;＝盼【史】</note><app n="0241011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">盼</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31097;</rdg></app>京都。私乃唯非
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a17"/>舍利神□□園。實是須□布金之
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a18"/>地。自非高見大士。十力世雄。安能
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a19"/>建斯功業者哉。　仰資帝祚永隆。
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a20"/>存沒父母。因緣眷屬。普蒙斯善。其
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a21"/>辭曰。<note n="0241012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30964;＝茫【史】</note><app n="0241012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">茫</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30964;</rdg></app>〃法水。眇眇零津。惠流<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB07099;</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a22"/>外。化被微　塵。三界有潤。火宅無
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a23"/>辛。杳〃真容。非人弗顯。苦樂憂悲。
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a24"/>非福不遣。刊石記功。以照諸善。
<lb ed="C I" n="0241a25"/>邑師比<note n="0241013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31098;＝丘【史】</note><app n="0241013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">丘</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31098;</rdg></app>淨敢起像<note n="0241014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31099;＝齋【史】</note><app n="0241014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">齋</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31099;</rdg></app>主張黃頭</p>
